reviews.review_text: Joan is proof that Donna wasn't that bad Anyone who complains about Donna should just give a listen to the acoustic set.  Joan Baez is a nice lady, but I just can't figure out this awful singing she has.  Case in point is Must've Been the Roses.  Great song all the way through until she joins in.  Awful, just awful.
